description.narrative:
Strengthening of the linkages and synergies between SGUA, the EEAS, and the Delegation regarding work on Ukraine's overall reform agenda and to contribute to the related strategic alignment and co-ordination of the EU's reform support. The annual Ukraine Reform Conference is one important factor in this regard.
EUs focal point for the above strategic and co-ordination tasks in the EU Delegation and ensure close co-ordination of relevant internal and external actors.
The Advisor would facilitate and contribute actively to overall reform co-ordination, including implementation of the Association Agreement/DCFTA, including through attending EU Member States' coordination meetings on the reform agenda in Kyiv.
